"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbdb5eaaf87ce0e69d6dba1e620276b71acd09d","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"help"},{"pid":"e8a26b25c820ab91d06effbf3c90b2a1f4480d79","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"help"},{"pid":"57a7c9cd4b83d9f556cf7c9811e75586a1fad30c","tid":412433,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對付癲佬你一定要癲過佢<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/001342_84281cd5d6ef66e7149f0f4d9ab04987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F001342_84281cd5d6ef66e7149f0f4d9ab04987.jpg&h=74404aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買一舊 開住佢<br />\n全家去一個星期旅行 返到黎佢全定會主動向你和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主都話果家人係癲<br />\n你因住佢癲起上黎拍你門無人應，唔知會做d 咩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班癲佬打爛你對門即刻報警<br />\n報完等警察調和之後再開舊震樓神器<br />\n震到班癲佬訓唔到教<br />\n直頭蒞個真人版俄羅斯睡眠實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝多個cam 係門口，拆你門咪報警告佢刑毀<br />\n有曬證據"},{"pid":"1fc52d8bc3317fb6218e88e670fb6851f463cdf1","tid":412433,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"樓主咩都唔做 cam又唔買<br />\n震樓神器又唔買 係咁叫人講解決方法有春用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1145a4acd4ed03270995e040f136016a8543da15","tid":412433,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"樓主 你google search ICCMW<br />\n之後搵間最近你住果頭的<br />\n再去果間ICCMW 同D 社工針針<br />\n睇下有冇得搞<br />\n<br />\n係沒精神科醫生出ge memo 情況下<br />\n警察好少何會做野"},{"pid":"3d7e6d8382c1efea49e518b450e5e93a23f27726","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咩都唔做 cam又唔買<br />\n震樓神器又唔買 係咁叫人講解決方法有春用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然可以特登鬥鳩佢，捕鳩佢。但入左一個人罪，仲有個仔呀都係癲癲地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係"},{"pid":"1214f8dcaae2ae82e2fbede082b21cf09913e97d","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主 你google search ICCMW<br />\n之後搵間最近你住果頭的<br />\n再去果間ICCMW 同D 社工針針<br />\n睇下有冇得搞<br />\n<br />\n係沒精神科醫生出ge memo 情況下<br />\n警察好少何會做野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efca2133b84523353e53601e0cca278635dfed2e","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主 你google search ICCMW<br />\n之後搵間最近你住果頭的<br />\n再去果間ICCMW 同D 社工針針<br />\n睇下有冇得搞<br />\n<br />\n係沒精神科醫生出ge memo 情況下<br />\n警察好少何會做野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n警察會做d咩，可以幫到我？？"},{"pid":"3a9e084cf0f36924bd882784d795cde836581d1f","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主 你google search ICCMW<br />\n之後搵間最近你住果頭的<br />\n再去果間ICCMW 同D 社工針針<br />\n睇下有冇得搞<br />\n<br />\n係沒精神科醫生出ge memo 情況下<br />\n警察好少何會做野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n警察會做d咩，可以幫到我？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想一劑斷尾，唔想拖落去，對唔住各位巴打我真係要諗過度過先可以做到，一陣出咩事真係承受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1759a65cdecfd53a46314dfd2beec3dca53cc978","tid":412433,"uid":13282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"拎白卡既話無好難搞，<br />\n不過你可以嘗試下由白色酸性液體果度入手"},{"pid":"07084d8d13e2b212f6abc93b094c5adb82962297","tid":412433,"uid":125107,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察會做d咩，可以幫到我？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知香港係唔係18區都係甘做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正常iccmw 開左file之後<br />\n佢地會試下家訪果個單位<br />\n<br />\n之後佢地覺得個case 係要睇精神科的話<br />\n佢地會拎個case 去醫管局精神科果到開會<br />\n<br />\n開會d 醫生覺得有需要就會出隊<br />\n<br />\n到時警察會帶case 去急症室<br />\n再安排d 治療比case"},{"pid":"eefc7ced20f61b7e01062a034fd74d539fa6df4a","tid":412433,"uid":13282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎白卡既話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係</span></strong>好難搞，<br />\n不過你可以嘗試下由白色酸性液體果度入手</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3c82f3a181f78e24d4093a99a7ba5e10187c36c4","tid":412433,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78a52c6163ec0ac5f7afa83328d227cc404a611e","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"20fc4cac0f2c4d92c97572b6c530fdfacfb84b77","tid":412433,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:06:22.000Z","msg":"殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9b7fa198c48ebf9b3de4a6495bb5613f0db19e","tid":412433,"uid":124756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:26:57.000Z","msg":"佢日日嘈 你就日日報警 講到自己生命嚴重受到威脅 等啲警察日日上門搵佢 事實上 個啲白色液體有機會真係會令你有生命威脅"},{"pid":"c764d5be5e967371f35c954a54532e0d4f46c60a","tid":412433,"uid":122637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"push"}]}